  "id": "9fT7HUaI",
  "slug": "improvable-skills",
  "title": "Improvable Skills",
  "description": "Adds skills and abilities that vastly upgrade players!",
  "body": "<p><strong>This mod requires&nbsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/hammer-lib\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://curseforge.zeith.org/api/v2/logo?id=247401\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />&nbsp;HammerLib</a>.</strong></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vC8fGUv.png\" width=\"676\" height=\"221\" /></p>\n<p>This is a complete re-write of old PlayerStats and PlayerStats 2 by <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Zeitheron</span>&nbsp;and xMrVizzy, but using new HammerLib.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This mod allows players to upgrade themselves using experience and <img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/improvableskills/skills_book.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Book of Skills.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Table of skills:</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/accelerated_furnace_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Accelerated Furnace:</strong> This skill increases the melting speed.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/alchemist_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Alchemist</strong>: This skill&nbsp;boosts the speed of the brewing stand.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/alchemist.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/attack_speed_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Attack Speed</strong>:&nbsp;This skill increases the strike speed of any tool/weapon.</li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/cutting_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Cutting:</strong> This skill increases the speed of the cutting axe.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/generic_protection_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Dense Skin</strong>: This skill makes your skin tougher against enemies (adds extra armor points).&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/generic_protection.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/dexterous_arms_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Dexterous Arms</strong>: This skill makes your tools and armor last longer.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/dexterous_arms.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/digging_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Digging:</strong> This skill&nbsp;increases the speed of the digging shovel.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/enchanter_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Enchanter</strong>: This skill decreases the minimal level required to enchant an item.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/enchanter.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/ender_manipulator_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Ender Manipulator</strong>: This skill reduces damage taken from the ender pearl.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/ender_manipulator.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/xp_plus_hovered.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Experience Harvesting</strong>: This skill increases&nbsp;obtainable experience from mining, breeding animals, fishing, and killing mobs.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/xp_plus.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/health_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Extra Health</strong>: This skill boosts your max health up to +20 HP (10 hearts).&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/health.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/growth_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Fast Growth</strong>:&nbsp;This skill randomly applies bone meal to surrounding plants.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/growth.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/fast_swimmer_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Fast Swimmer:</strong> This skill increases the movement speed in water.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/huckster_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Huckster:</strong> This skill reduces villager trading prices.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/huckster.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/ladder_king_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;King of the Ladder:</strong> This skill increases the speed while climbing on ladders.</li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/leaper_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Leaper:</strong> This skill increases the height of the jump player.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/luck_of_the_sea_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Luck of The Sea</strong>: This skill lures fish to your fishing hook.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/luck_of_the_sea.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/mining_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Mining:</strong> This skill increases the speed of the mining pickaxe.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/obsidian_skin_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Obsidian Skin:</strong> This skill reduces fire/lava damage taken.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/obsidian_skin.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/pvp_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;PvP Protection</strong>: This skill decreases PvP-type damage taken.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/atkdmg_ranged_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Sharp Arrow</strong>: This skill increases ranged damage dealt to any entity.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/atkdmg_ranged.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/silent_foot_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Silent Foot</strong>: This skill reduces the radius of any vibrations you make.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/silent_foot.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/soft_landing_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Soft Landing:</strong> This skill reduces the damage from falling players.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/soul_speed_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Soul Speed</strong>: This skill increases movement speed on soul sand, but damages your boots as if they had the enchantment.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/soul_speed.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/atkdmg_melee_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;</strong><strong>Strong Fist</strong>: This skill&nbsp;increases melee damage dealt to any entity.</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/treasure_sands_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Treasure of the Sands</strong>: This skill allows one to find treasures from the sand.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/renders/skill_scrolls/treasure_sands.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></li>\n<li><del><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/skills/ore_finder_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #800000;\">Treasure</span> Finder:</strong>&nbsp;This skill allows players to find precious resources, while mining.</span></del></li>\n<li><del><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>Item Repairer</strong>: This skill slowly repairs items in both hands and worn armor.</span></del></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\n<h1>Table of abilities:</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/abilities/auto_xp_bank_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Auto XP Bank:</strong> This ability allows you to keep the exact amount of levels with you at all times, while storing excess into the XP Bank.</li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/abilities/anvil_normal.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Blacksmith:</strong> This ability opens up repair menu, which acts completely like the regular anvil.</li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/abilities/crafter_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Crafter:</strong> This ability opens up 3x3 crafting menu, which acts completely like the regular crafting table.</li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/abilities/enchanting_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Crafter:</strong> This ability opens up the enchanting menu. You can click the 'Enchant Power' label to improve the level of your portable enchanting table.</li>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/abilities/magnetism_hovered.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Magnetism:</strong> This ability allows you to enable a magnet that sucks all items within the configurable range towards you.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\n<h1>Extra little things:</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dragon-forge/ImprovableSkills/master/src/main/resources/assets/improvableskills/textures/item/parchment_fragment.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" />&nbsp;Parchment Fragment:</strong> This item allows creating ability scrolls above. See the in-game tooltip for ability scrolls, or item usages in JEI.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h5><strong>Thanks to the following people:</strong></h5>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://curseforge.com/members/Shalazhar_13\">Shalazhar_13 (Khaoss)</a> - Spanish translation</strong></li>\n<li><strong><a title=\"Linkout to GitHub\" href=\"https://github.com/ACGaming\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ACGaming</a> - German translation</strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://curseforge.com/members/Yukensha\">Yukensha</a> - Sprites</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LuJJMv1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"698\" height=\"1\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Permissions:</strong></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You&nbsp;can use this mod in your modpack.</strong></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You are not allowed to re-publish this mod to other sites without providing a Modrinth/CurseForge download link and my permission (PM to <a href=\"https://me.zeith.gay/\"><img src=\"https://assets.zeith.org/icons/zeitheron.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />&nbsp;Zeitheron</a>, or via Discord)</strong></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You are not allowed to include this (or any other mods of the DragonForge team) in your own mod. Building add-ons, however, is allowed, but a friendly PM would be good.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>The only supported version of Minecraft is the latest one that this mod exists for. DO NOT ASK TO DOWNGRADE!</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" href=\"https://ds.zeith.org/dev\"><img src=\"https://ds.zeith.org/cards/dev.png\" width=\"510\" height=\"170\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Want to discuss anything? Need help with APIs?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Join the discord server and follow Zeitheron on <a href=\"http://bit.ly/ZeithTwitter\"><img src=\"https://abs.twimg.com/favicons/twitter.ico\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />Twitter</a>!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>If you would like to support my work, you can become a patron via <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/zeitheron\"><img src=\"https://c5.patreon.com/external/favicon/favicon-32x32.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Patreon</a>.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/pix.iemoji.com/twit33/0744.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"33\" height=\"33\" /></strong></p>",
